Class StackLayoutPanel

java.lang.Object

                  org.gwt.mosaic.ui.client.StackLayoutPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.google.gwt.user.client.EventListener, HasLayoutManager
public class StackLayoutPanel
extends LayoutComposite

A layout panel that stacks its children vertically, displaying only one at a time, with a header for each child which the user can click to display.

CSS Style Rules

  • .mosaic-StackLayoutPanel { the panel itself }
  • .mosaic-StackLayoutPanel .mosaic-StackLayoutPanelItem { unselected items }
  • .mosaic-StackLayoutPanel .mosaic-StackLayoutPanelItem-selected { selected items }
  • .mosaic-StackLayoutPanel .mosaic-StackLayoutPanelContent { the wrapper around the contents of the item }
